{"type":"message","id":"e7e71082","parentId":"f828870e","timestamp":"2026-04-06T09:19:44.497Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to follow the user's instructions to fix the heartbeat health monitor. They said:\n\n1. Remove --announce from heartbeat-health-monitor (stops duplicate alerts):\n   openclaw cron list\n   # Find heartbeat-health-monitor job ID, then:\n   openclaw cron edit <job-id> --announce false\n\n2. Clear stale critical alerts:\n   # Send a group message (updates group_message)\n   message(action=send, channel=telegram, target=-1003606834639, text=\"Hey Nrexya! Quick check-in 🖤\")\n   # Run git backup manually (updates git_push)\n   cd ~/.openclaw/workspace\n   git add -A\n   git commit -m \"manual backup - clearing stale state\"\n   git push origin master\n\n3. Verify health monitor:\n   python3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/heartbeat_health_cron.py --dry-run\n   This should show no critical issues after the fixes.\n\nLet me do these steps one by one.\n\nFirst, I need to get the job ID for heartbeat-health-monitor from the cron list. Looking at the cron list output above, I can see the heartbeat-health-monitor job has id: \"eeef1692-7e97-45f3-ad50-814f0afcae29\"\n\nNow I need to edit this job to set --announce false. Looking at the current payload, it's:\n\"message\": \"python3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/heartbeat_health_cron.py\"\n\nI need to change this to remove the --announce flag, but wait - the --announce flag is not in the message. The user said to remove --announce from heartbeat-health-monitor. Looking at the job definition, I see:\n\"delivery\": {\n  \"mode\": \"announce\",\n  \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n  \"to\": \"7924461837\"\n}\n\nAh, I see! The delivery mode is \"announce\". The user wants to change this from \"announce\" to \"none\" to stop duplicate alerts. So I need to edit the job to change delivery.mode from \"announce\" to \"none\".\n\nLet me do that now.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-81748afa86d1b171","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"edit","jobId":"eeef1692-7e97-45f3-ad50-814f0afcae29","patch":{"delivery":{"mode":"none"}}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free","usage":{"input":93334,"output":1040,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94374,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775467137401,"responseId":"gen-1775467138-ykdRAkqNTdNPJcSiJlU3"}}
