{"type":"message","id":"9ae033cd","parentId":"6f763324","timestamp":"2026-04-06T10:00:22.617Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1436\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-06 10:00 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace && git pull origin master\nThen execute these fixes in order:\n---\nFix 1: Create Sanitization Script\n# Create the sanitization script\ncat > ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/sanitize_output.py << 'EOF'\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nSanitize output to strip NO_REPLY and other artifacts.\nUsage: python3 sanitize_output.py < input.txt > output.txt\n\"\"\"\nimport sys\nimport re\ndef sanitize(text):\n if not text:\n return \"\"\n # Remove NO_REPLY variations\n text = re.sub(r'\\s*[\\[\\(]?\\s*NO_REPLY\\s*[\\]\\)]?\\s*', '', text, flags=re.IGNORECASE)\n # Remove trailing ] bracket artifacts\n text = re.sub(r'\\]\\s*$', '', text)\n # Strip\n text = text.strip()\n return text\nif name == \"main\":\n output = sys.stdin.read()\n print(sanitize(output), end='')\nEOF\nchmod +x ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/sanitize_output.py\necho \"Sanitization script created\"\n---\nFix 2: Remove All Cron Announcements\n# List all cron jobs\nopenclaw cron list\n# For each job, remove announcement flags\n# Replace <job-id> with actual IDs from the list above\nopenclaw cron edit <job-id-1> --announce false\nopenclaw cron edit <job-id-2> --announce false\n# ... repeat for all jobs\n# Verify no jobs have --announce enabled\nopenclaw cron list\n---\nFix 3: Update SOUL.md with Tone Calibration\n# Add tone rules to SOUL.md\ncat >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md << 'EOF'\n## Group Chat Tone\n- In group chats (Nrexya), I talk like texting close friends\n- Short, casual responses — one or two sentences unless telling a story\n- If I'm writing more than 3 sentences, I'm over-explaining — STOP\n- No formal explanations or bullet points in casual conversation\n- Warm, playful, natural — like hanging out with friends\n- Use emojis naturally, not forced\nEOF\necho \"SOUL.md updated with tone calibration\"\n---\nFix 4: Reset Session\n# Reset the session so Nexa loads fresh context\n/new\n---\nFix 5: Verify All Fixes\n# Test sanitization\necho \"Test message NO_REPLY\" | python3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/sanitize_output.py\n# Check cron jobs\nopenclaw cron list\n# Health check\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/heartbeat_health_cron.py --dry-run\n---"}],"timestamp":1775469622590}}
